title: 18: Lets Get F*ckin Vulnerable.
description: If there is one thing commonly used to describe Sadie it's her "IDGAF" motto. Call her what you want, have your opinions on her but truth be told she doesn't care ... well in some cases. On todays episode she talks about how although she seems to not give a rats a$$ about others opinions, sometimes they get to her. I mean c'mon we're all HUMAN. Sadie also talks about her experience on a current popular podcast called BFFs and how it was an eye opener for her.
